{"tid":648430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蟒蛇女勒死果子狸  清水灣街坊嚇窒","createTime":"2018-04-30T16:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T01:51:37.000Z","uid":28366,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"725d5395d91a7140945e60af3ac54c5202b0f75d","tid":648430,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/002421_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F002421_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=25dc4c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">蛇王何嚟到將條蟒蛇捉走。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/002437_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F002437_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9907a1dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">果子狸俾條大蟒蛇纏死咗</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/002500_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F002500_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=13da25f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">一班街坊走晒出去路邊圍觀。</span><br />\n<br />\n大自然嘅規則就係弱肉強食，適者生存，而喺夜晚清水灣碧水新村就正正上演呢一幕！星期一晚10點幾，讀者阿恆見到一隻半米長嘅果子狸喺路邊，郁都唔郁，而佢嘅身上就俾條大約12呎長嘅蟒蛇纏住，搞到一地血，嚇到幾十個居民走出嚟圍觀。其中一個街坊話30年前就喺屋企出面條大坑渠，見過一條大蟒蛇，估唔到而家又見到，仲笑笑口話唔知而家呢條大蟒蛇，係咪以前嗰一條。<br />\n<br />\n一班街坊係咁話當年，搞到準備開大餐嘅大蟒蛇都滴晒汗，不停郁身郁勢，好似好唔好意思咁，當住佢哋面醫吓五臟廟。蛇王何奉召嚟到，迅速活擒大蟒蛇，蛇王何話呢條係緬甸蟒蛇女，4到5歲左右，估計果子狸喺叢林搵食嗰陣，俾蛇女睇中，糾纏之下碌出馬路，果子狸最後亦被勒死，但係蛇王何認為村民走近圍觀令蛇女受驚，未必吞到隻果子狸。蟒蛇交咗畀警方，之後會轉交嘉道理農場安排野放。<br />\n<br />\n雖然今次呢條蛇女食唔到隻果子狸，不過睇返資料，2007年嗰陣西貢井欄樹就有條10呎長嘅緬甸蟒，偷偷竄入村入面嘅農莊，纏死咗隻小黑草羊，之後仲成隻吞咗，但無幾耐又嘔返出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸蟒係世界上最巨型嘅6種蛇類之一，喺亞洲算係屬於第二大蛇，主要棲息喺近水地方同樹上，同屬於夜行性動物嘅果子狸一樣，都係受《野生動物保護條例》第170章保護，唔可以捕獵。而果子狸主要分布喺大嶼山同新界西北以外郊區，平日行蹤好隱秘，唔鍾意喺人類面前出現，所以大家如果想見到果子狸都有一定難度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180501/58138407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58138407&d=CKP6R7xOsIMcEqWMGR%2ByKNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=97f3f431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58138407&h=af2aec3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180501/58138407</a>"},{"pid":"ba8bbd1f688ca2c4644e82d447f57ddd6c48a101","tid":648430,"uid":12404,"like":1,"dislike":55,"score":-54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"果子狸仲得人閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05f85faf33ab4559f48232485b0a2cd9c686099","tid":648430,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"野放？ 即係送落中果忍個肚咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6da19b62f35b817bfba3e515f364c702f8874c9","tid":648430,"uid":33213,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"d05f85faf33ab4559f48232485b0a2cd9c686099","tid":648430,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"野放？ 即係送落中果忍個肚咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:33:23.000Z","msg":"本身都係野生<br />\n你想點<br />\n<br />\n捉佢返屋企養?"},{"pid":"103bb3b256b6deb34fbb1beffa5319c92af8776d","tid":648430,"uid":25834,"like":122,"dislike":16,"score":106,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"香港冇原生蟒蛇，係啲人走失或者放生<br />\n唔應該再係香港放生"},{"pid":"61f14a045041dc61cff655052301c758864d9925","tid":648430,"uid":113178,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":